#

Pork and Vegetable Skewers

30 min
$15
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Soy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

GrillingQuick MealHealthy

Description

Juicy pork and colorful vegetables grilled to perfection on skewers, perfect for a quick and tasty meal!

Ingredients

  • pork tenderloin: 1 lb
  • bell peppers (red, green, or yellow): 2
  • zucchini: 1
  • red onion: 1
  • cherry tomatoes: 1 cup
  • olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • soy sauce: 2 tbsp
  • garlic (minced): 2 cloves
  • black pepper: to taste
  • salt: to taste
  • paprika: 1 tsp
  • oregano: 1 tsp
